- 21apr12-1232 G Categorise per prefix in logs
  - I Redundant but also cleary distinguishable types / workflows
    - ! With depending paths
    - Types 
      - .bashrc
        - "Must-haves" for all situations
        - Prefix: ".bashrc:"
      - Tools (for /usr/local/bin)
        - too small to make XZM
        - too frequent changes to make XZM
          - esp. as tool collection in one XZM
          - Prefix: "Tools:"
      - Setttings (for programs)
        - For programs from "System" (Xfce / onboard) and user XZMs
          - on rootcopy more flexible than as part of XZM
          - Prefix: "Settings: PROGRAM:"
      - Extensions (for programs)
        - see Settings
        - Prefix: "Extensions: PROGRAM:"
